docs.lead_paragraph: THE tourist who, likes to keep on the move and pack a continent at a time into his sight-seeing jaunts should try a six-week whirl through South America. It is a challenging venture. The special forty-five-day, roundtrip air fare helps keep the cost down and the dollar goes a long way in most Latin-American countries.
